      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for 2018 Lexus RX 350 in an elegant Nebula Gray Pearl. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, though it shows minor, typical road peppering on the front bumper and one small door ding on the rear passenger side\u2014hardly noticeable but mentioned for full transparency. Inside, the Parchment leather interior is exceptionally clean; the seats show only light bolster wear, and the cabin remains a strictly smoke-free environment. All tech features, including the premium navigation system and heated/ventilated seats, function perfectly. Under the hood, the V6 engine runs smoothly, backed by a comprehensive service history. We recently completed a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection, confirming the brakes and tires have plenty of life remaining. This is a dependable, premium SUV that has been maintained with an open checkbook and is ready for its next owner.",
